*  Please read this release note before you run StarRC!!!

*  LVS DECK
   Please use SmicSP2R_cal40_LL_sali_p1mtx_11182533_V1.14_0.lvs_for_cci LVS deck for CCI-StarRC extraction.

*  Revision: Version 1.14_0

*  Calibre Version for Validation : calibre_2013.1_14.11

*  StarXtract Version for Test : G-2012.06-SP1

*  GRDGENXO Version for Generation : G-2012.06-SP1

*  CONTENTS:
   This Release_Note is available for SMIC 40nm LLRF Salicide 1.1V/1.8V/2.5V & 1.1V/1.8V/3.3V process.
   The metal scheme includes:
	1TM(9K)		  1P4M/ 5M/ 6M/ 7M/ 8M/ 9M
	1MTT(34K)	  1P4M/ 5M/ 6M/ 7M/ 8M/ 9M
	2TM(9K) 	  1P4M/ 5M/ 6M/ 7M/ 8M/ 9M/ 10M
	1TM(9K)+1MTT(34K) 1P4M/ 5M/ 6M/ 7M/ 8M/ 9M/ 10M

*  Release Date: 2015/09/14	17:00:00

   1) ITF/*.itf
      the itf file used to generate *.nxtgrd file. Transistor-level ITF is compatible with cell-level extraction no matter what kind of extraction flow is used.

   2) NXTGRD/*.nxtgrd
      the TCAD file used in star_cmd. Transistor-level ITF is compatible with cell-level extraction no matter what kind of extraction flow is used.

   3) CCI_flow
      This folder includes all the files only used for CCI-StarRC flow. 
      xxx_cell.map  cell level mappping for Astro techfile.
      xxx_tran_CCI.map is for Calibre-StarRC transistor level extraction flow only, should be included in CCI_cmd.
      query_cmd creats a collection of Calibre Connectivity Interface(CCI) input files.
      CCI_cmd is the command file for CCI-StarRC extraction.
      Please choose the correct mapping file based on your process target and set star_cmd correctly.

   5) Release_Note
      This file.

